        "content": "<p>That would would probably be better as \"View messages sent by xyz\" or \"messages by xyz\"...<br>\nAnd there is probably a better icon than that one. Can't think of one on the spot though.<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/74/DcsTYqpwc5tw7dGyreyo5aGJ/image.png\" title=\"image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/74/DcsTYqpwc5tw7dGyreyo5aGJ/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/74/DcsTYqpwc5tw7dGyreyo5aGJ/image.png\"></a></div>",
